{"tid":2152691,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］父親因買錯報紙被兒襲擊","createTime":"2020-08-12T06:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T07:44:24.000Z","uid":128413,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6da6aaaa595177348f775d91a80aabe5c47659","tid":2152691,"uid":128413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:37:17.000Z","msg":"日本警視廳於12日以傷害罪嫌疑，在東京都中野區，逮捕了一名以類似鈍器的物體毆打父親的的少年（15歲）。由於母親看到兒子的暴行而馬上加以阻止，父親只受了輕傷。<br />\n根據調查，少年和父親（42歲）約好，要父親替他購買於8月11日發售的蘋果日報。不過從早上就去排隊的父親，卻買回了東荒日報，這讓少年相當惱火。在吃早飯時，少年拿起放在餐桌上的水果刀旁邊的法式麵包（長30厘米），不斷毆打父親。<br />\n<br />\n聽到父親的慘叫的母親急忙來阻止了少年，不過父親的額頭還是受了輕微的毆傷。少年被附近接到報告的警察逮捕。在調查中少年供訴到：「一想到他那麼早出去到底去排了什麼隊，就惱火的不得了。」<br />\n<br />\n警視廳表示，今後類似這種由於親子間對報章的理解溝通不充分，而引發的暴力事件，還將有可能發生，請大家引以為戒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上內容純粹虛構"},{"pid":"5f381815df98ef71e5f66702c23d26c4bbb94f98","tid":2152691,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n以下內容純粹虛構"},{"pid":"525bb516d98a530f342576e1d8266d82e4ab60fa","tid":2152691,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"改潮文都要驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f6c91f67ea536fdd13dc0c73c058b5e335088e","tid":2152691,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"525bb516d98a530f342576e1d8266d82e4ab60fa","tid":2152691,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"改潮文都要驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"買錯報都要驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36bc3ea20022d1a5f3f8f42602f9cb6fb91e328","tid":2152691,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}